[[File:NBL.jpg|thumb|A game of Nuna-ball.]]

The [[The galaxy/Legends|galaxy's]] first professional '''[[Nuna-ball/Legends|Nuna-Ball]] League (NBL)''' was established by [[Lysko Buelia]] and a group of investors, during the [[Standard year/Legends|years]] leading up to the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

Teams in the league were made up entirely of [[Droid/Legends|droids]], with new models of droids being grouped into teams and pitted against each other in matches that mimicked the organic sport.

Droid manufacturers liked this format for many reasons, one of which was the minimal cost involved in fielding a team versus the monetary rewards of the sport's popularity.

